      "content": "it's not just about pressure. it's that there's nothing left to even give. it feels like the story is just... finished. like i've reached the end of the book and the pages are just blank now. what is the point of just \"being still\" when there's nothing left inside to be still with? it feels like i'm just haunting my own life.",
